Ya, janggut Ortodoks Rusia awak,
Serbia celaka.

378
00:28:26,083 --> 00:28:27,916
Atau janggut Jeremiah Johnson?

379
00:28:28,916 --> 00:28:31,583
Di mana keldai bodoh itu?
Tertinggal di mana?

380
00:28:32,333 --> 00:28:34,583
- Saya nampak, gemuk.
- Mata satu lagi.

381
00:28:46,333 --> 00:28:50,083
Jangan risau, ia belum pulih.
Esok mesti lebih jelas.

382
00:28:51,458 --> 00:28:52,708
Pakai penutup semula.

383
00:29:00,166 --> 00:29:01,625
Saya ambilkan tongkat.

384
00:29:11,000 --> 00:29:12,041
Palermo?

385
00:29:20,375 --> 00:29:22,833
- Mata Helang sedang dengar.
- Tokyo ada?

386
00:29:26,125 --> 00:29:27,333
Ya, dia ada di sini.

387
00:29:40,500 --> 00:29:41,333
Profesor.

388
