Tokyo,

389
00:29:46,250 --> 00:29:47,500
Rio ada di Sepanyol.

390
00:29:59,041 --> 00:29:59,916
Terima kasih.

391
00:30:01,791 --> 00:30:03,375
Semoga dapat peluk awak

392
00:30:04,083 --> 00:30:06,208
dan ucap terima kasih tak lama lagi.

393
00:30:07,208 --> 00:30:08,041
Tentulah.

394
00:30:13,541 --> 00:30:17,000
Kerja paling sukar masih di depan
tapi kita akan berjaya.

395
00:30:18,666 --> 00:30:19,916
Kita akan jayakannya.

396
00:30:32,875 --> 00:30:33,958
Semua perbuatan,

397
00:30:35,000 --> 00:30:37,125
semuanya ada akibat.

398
00:30:37,708 --> 00:30:39,041
Bagi pihak polis pula?

399
