00:31:53,416 --> 00:31:54,250
Ya.

425
00:31:56,625 --> 00:31:58,375
Awak bekerja dengan dia.

426
00:31:58,833 --> 00:32:01,250
Teliti isyarat ini. Abaikan yang lain.

427
00:32:01,375 --> 00:32:02,583
Baiklah.

428
00:32:02,666 --> 00:32:05,083
Ini rahsia kita. Jangan beritahu sesiapa.

429
00:32:25,291 --> 00:32:28,250
Seronoknya dapat bercuti
hujung minggu macam ini.

430
00:32:29,666 --> 00:32:31,708
Tanpa perlu rompak apa-apa.

431
00:32:31,791 --> 00:32:33,333
Ya, pergi berbulan madu.

432
00:32:33,416 --> 00:32:34,625
Ya.

433
00:32:36,416 --> 00:32:38,958
Kalau begitu, kita perlu berkahwin dulu.

434
00:32:39,416 --> 00:32:42,541
