Itu apa, lamaran pengecut?

438
00:32:52,041 --> 00:32:54,666
Kenapa awak lempar batu, sembunyi tangan?

439
00:32:54,750 --> 00:32:56,250
- Cakap saja.
- Sudah.

440
00:32:56,333 --> 00:32:58,208
Awak semakin burukkan keadaan.

441
00:32:59,166 --> 00:33:00,291
Hubungi Marseille.

442
00:33:01,708 --> 00:33:02,541
Baiklah.

443
00:33:02,625 --> 00:33:03,500
Hei.

444
00:33:04,458 --> 00:33:06,250
Kalau nak ajak saya kahwin,

445
00:33:07,250 --> 00:33:09,041
lain kali melamar betul-betul.

446
00:33:12,291 --> 00:33:13,791
Cari tempat berhenti.

447
00:33:49,666 --> 00:33:51,208
Inspektor, dia telefon.

448
00:34:03,958 --> 00:34:04,833
Profesor.

449
00:34:07,416 --> 00:34:10,583
Inspektor Sierra? Seronoknya!
