450
00:34:11,958 --> 00:34:15,083
Ya, saya tahu awak suka berunding
dengan polis wanita.

451
00:34:15,666 --> 00:34:17,750
Tak nak tanya saya pakai apa?

452
00:34:18,416 --> 00:34:19,791
Baju ibu hamil?

453
00:34:19,875 --> 00:34:22,208
Awak memang kolot!

454
00:34:22,916 --> 00:34:25,208
Awak jenis lelaki yang pakai singlet?

455
00:34:25,416 --> 00:34:27,458
Sebenarnya, ya, tapi...

456
00:34:29,166 --> 00:34:31,833
Gaya klasik tak lapuk dek zaman. Setuju?

